description: Posts time series data points to Amazon DataZone for the specified asset.

parameters.name: clientToken
parameters.description: A unique, case-sensitive identifier that is provided to ensure the idempotency of the request. This field is autopopulated if not provided.

parameters.name: domainIdentifier
parameters.description: The ID of the Amazon DataZone domain in which you want to post time series data points.

parameters.name: entityIdentifier
parameters.description: The ID of the asset for which you want to post time series data points.

parameters.name: entityType
parameters.description: The type of the asset for which you want to post data points.

parameters.name: forms
parameters.description: The forms that contain the data points that you want to post. (dict) --- The time series data points form. content (string) --- The content of the time series data points form. The name of the time series data points form. The timestamp of the time series data points form. The ID of the type of the time series data points form. typeRevision (string) --- The revision type of the time series data points form.

nested_params.description: The content of the time series data points form.

nested_params.description: The timestamp of the time series data points form.

nested_params.name: typeIdentifier

nested_params.name: typeRevision
nested_params.description: The revision type of the time series data points form.
